UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2464
1 Section 1. The members of the Senate hereby designate the week of May 17 to
2 23, 2026, as National Public Works Week, to celebrate and recognize the hard work and
3 dedication of the public works professionals across the Commonwealth.
4 Section 2. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
5 Resolution to Senator Steve Rawlings.
